text: Inge Senoner (born 21 February 1940) is an Italian alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Italy Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Santa Cristina Gherdëina
